title: Open Weekends For Tour - Renovated - Luxury Amenities - Great Location
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Three, Lighted Tennis Courts Featuring a Versacourt System', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
